reviews.review_text:
Great matrix of a nice show Nice work. Cool 1/2 Step, Rooster, Great Cassidy. Rockin' second set too.

I'd love to hear a matrix of the previous night too. 6/8/92 is another great Richfield show ripe for matrixing.

Thanks!
